  {
	"bg": "#f5ede9",
	"illustration": "res://assets/images/opening_overpass.png",
	"speed": 1.0,
	"speaker": "",
	"text": "秋天的下午，天橋上的風帶著一點點涼意。"
  },
  {
	"bg": "#f5ede9",
	"illustration": "res://assets/images/opening_overpass.png",
	"speaker": "女同學",
	"text": "欸，妳還帶著這個舊時鐘喔？都要畢業了耶。"
