  {
	"bg": "#e8d7a5",
	"illustration": "res://assets/images/opening_decesnt.png",
	"shake": true,
	"speaker": "",
	"text": "幾個打鬧的小學生撞過肩頭。那一瞬間，指尖感受到了冰冷的空氣。"
