  {
	"bg": "#292a3b",
	"flash": true,
	"shake": true,
	"speed": 2.0,
	"speaker": "",
	"text": "我撲向了天橋的邊緣。然後，世界徹底失去了重力。"
  },
  {
	"bg": "#ffffff",
	"flash": true,
	"speed": 4.0,
	"speaker": "",
	"text": "⋯⋯⋯⋯"
  },
  {
	"bg": "#393632",
	"illustration": "res://assets/images/opening_factory.png",
	"speed": 2.0,
	"speaker": "",
	"text": "意識恢復的時候，空氣裡滿是塵埃與鐵鏽的味道。"
  },
  {
	"bg": "#393632",
	"illustration": "res://assets/images/opening_factory.png",
	"speed": 1.5,
	"speaker": "",
	"text": "很安靜。那是連呼吸聲都聽不見的，寂靜。"
  },
  {
	"bg": "#393632",
	"illustration": "res://assets/images/opening_factory.png",
	"speed": 1.0,
	"speaker": "主角",
	"text": "（做夢了嗎⋯⋯？）"
