  {
	"bg": "#393632",
	"illustration": "res://assets/images/opening_factory.png",
	"speed": 2.0,
	"speaker": "",
	"text": "低頭一看，映入眼簾的，是一雙佈滿粗糙縫線的、玩偶的手。"
