  {
	"bg": "#393632",
	"illustration": "res://assets/images/opening_factory.png",
	"speed": 2.0,
	"speaker": "主角",
	"text": "（我變成了⋯⋯玩偶？）"
  },
  {
	"bg": "#393632",
	"illustration": "res://assets/images/opening_factory.png",
	"speed": 2.5,
	"speaker": "",
	"text": "在這座廢棄的工廠裡，連時間似乎都乾涸了。"
