  {
	"bg": "#393632",
	"illustration": "res://assets/images/opening_factory.png",
	"speed": 1.0,
	"speaker": "",
	"text": "而在不遠處的齒輪堆裡，我看到了一個熟悉的身影。"
  },
  {
	"bg": "#393632",
	"illustration": "res://assets/images/opening_factory.png",
	"shake": true,
	"speed": 2.0,
	"speaker": "",
	"text": "他坐在那裡。面盤破裂、指針遺失，像是壞掉了很久很久。"
  },
  {
	"bg": "#393632",
	"illustration": "res://assets/images/opening_factory.png",
	"speed": 3.0,
	"speaker": "主角",
	"text": "「吶，說好了喔⋯⋯」"
